{"tid":408243,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我返工個位比人鳩佔","createTime":"2017-09-21T05:25:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-02T15:06:24.000Z","uid":148659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0a8cbfedb5c43a3afb6c9526ae79c192666511b2","tid":408243,"uid":148659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T05:25:30.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我係文員仔，公司每人有張枱，大概5呎長<br />\n我份人比較企理乾淨，枱面得printer,電腦,keyboard <br />\n文具嘢，零食，公司file 我習慣收入櫃，<br />\n所以張台都淨返好多位，<br />\n公司好大塵，唔知係咪因為中央冷氣污糟，<br />\n隔2,3日張枱就會舖塵，所以每日返工都會抹下先<br />\n啲同事唔知係咪葡萄我張台乾淨，<br />\n一行過就會擺底啲文件喺我張台，話擺低先<br />\n行過又會將杯水擺低，<br />\n試過有人買外賣仲將啲油淋淋外賣擺去我張台，話放住先，等陣拎返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n隔離位同事張台好撚多嘢，有一日，佢趕住同人傾project,佢print左一大疊note擺去我個位度，之後專登喺我個位度釘notes <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢仲試過趁我去廁所，佢自己位唔坐，霸左我個位成個鐘，我當時趕住做project但所有嘢喺電腦度，佢話: 借個位黎先我都趕時間做project,你個位多位啲<br />\ndiu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人人個位一樣大架啦，搞到我on99走左去廁所坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老闆仲on99，有次走黎同隔離位個同事傾計，佢見我張枱有位，成個屎忽坐落張台度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a6d9cc9a96622711a5967c38b8c8eb6aec9372e","tid":408243,"uid":75692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T05:26:39.000Z","msg":"你係咪打雜?"},{"pid":"8ac1b8e8b0780aeae9ffc0458e72ec483ba85869","tid":408243,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T05:34:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f01bb03424dd71382d78d7785253f16b0b929b71","tid":408243,"uid":53126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T05:44:49.000Z","msg":"放返D野上枱度囉～"},{"pid":"69c9342b4e19155b8bb9dc1d5bf5f96064df554b","tid":408243,"uid":148659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T05:49:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係咪打雜?</blockquote><br />\n唔係呀，我都好似其他同事咁，跟下啲project"},{"pid":"4ffb6e66cf2b7825e10a3bce4f1d33f7199bfc45","tid":408243,"uid":148659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T05:49:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打工仔係咁嫁啦  出聲都無用  老闆唔睇你有咩計</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cf9dd74397b9c36c61aba05fb7ee14d32df8947","tid":408243,"uid":148659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T05:50:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>放返D野上枱度囉～</blockquote><br />\n有得諗，我都諗住放返啲文具上枱"},{"pid":"f993f79ced873a4e2f1e0296459f6a1ba5996ae2","tid":408243,"uid":89665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T06:25:04.000Z","msg":"可能佢地串鳩你冇野做"},{"pid":"deff5445331d1295e7a0e8a8683fc9aa04e95cc6","tid":408243,"uid":36927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T06:31:09.000Z","msg":"放到成張枱滿晒野"},{"pid":"c16e69c65231800a6a1eef7ddbad0b7e857df24e","tid":408243,"uid":32439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T06:38:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>放返D野上枱度囉～</blockquote><br />\n有得諗，我都諗住放返啲文具上枱</blockquote><br />\n睇錯放啲文員上枱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c6fc877a9419c3d0e8af72667d1e1f11c2b01b5","tid":408243,"uid":19271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T15:06:24.000Z","msg":"放哂啲零食喺枱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}